  ],
  "remarks": "Yury Nimchenko has been a Senator of the Federation Council from the illegally annexed “Republic of Crimea” since 12 September 2024 and is a Member of the Federation Council’s Committee on Defence and Security. He is a veteran of Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine, having fought as a tank driver, for which he was awarded the title of “Hero of Russia” by the President of the Russian Federation",
